DIFFICULT, NOT IMPOSSIBLE.

00:00:35.936 --> 00:00:38.038
&gt;&gt; WE HAVE THE RIGHT TO
PROTEST, THEY GO ON THE

00:00:38.071 --> 00:00:40.407
